did.head: Collection Summary

repository.corpname: Woodson Research Center, Rice University, Houston, Texas

did.unittitle: EOS: "Transactions of the American Geophysical Union" records
did.abstract: This collection contains articles and book reviews submitted to the publication "Transactions of the American Geophysical Union." Also included are office records, correspondence, SPR news, cover and meeting reports related to this publication of the AGU.

bioghist.head: Biographical Note
bioghist.p: Dr. Patricia H. Reiff is a Professor in the Department of Physics and Astronomy at Rice University. She served as Editor of EOS: "Transactions of the American Geophysical Union" publication from 1986-1989. She is also a Fellow of the American Geophysical Union and Director of the Rice Space Institute.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This collection contains articles and book reviews submitted to the publication "Transactions of the American Geophysical Union." Dr. Patricia Reiff served as editor of this publication from 1985-1989, and the collection also contains office records, correspondence, SPR news, covers and meeting reports as they relate to her editorship of this publication.

userestrict.head: Restrictions on Use
userestrict.p: Permission to publish material from the EOS: "Transactions of the American Geophysical Union" records must be obtained from the Woodson Research Center, Fondren Library.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: This collection was a gift donated by Dr. Patricia Reiff, Editor, Solar-Planetary Relationships and EOS, in February of 1992.
